<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <%- include('./partials/header') %>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.1/font/bootstrap-icons.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, sans-serif;
        }

        .access-denied-container {
            max-width: 800px;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 24px;
            padding: 60px 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            text-align: center;
        }

        .lock-icon {
            width: 120px;
            height: 120px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 30px;
        }

        .lock-icon i {
            font-size: 60px;
            color: white;
        }

        .main-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .sub-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #86868b;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .features-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .feature-box {
            background: #f5f5f7;
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 24px;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .feature-box.locked {
            opacity: 0.6;
            position: relative;
        }

        .feature-box.locked::before {
            content: '\f4fc';
            font-family: 'bootstrap-icons';
            position: absolute;
            top: 16px;
            right: 16px;
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #ff3b30;
        }

        .feature-title {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1d1d1f;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        .feature-desc {
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #86868b;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .cta-box {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            border-radius: 16px;
            padding: 32px;
            color: white;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .cta-title {
            font-size: 1.3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 12px;
        }

        .cta-desc {
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            opacity: 0.9;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        .btn-join {
            background: white;
            color: #667eea;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-join:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            color: #667eea;
        }

        .btn-back {
            background: transparent;
            color: #86868b;
            border: 1px solid #d2d2d7;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 12px 28px;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn-back:hover {
            background: #f5f5f7;
            color: #1d1d1f;
        }

        .price-tag {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            padding: 8px 16px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="access-denied-container">
        <div class="lock-icon">
            <i class="bi bi-lock-fill"></i>
        </div>

        <h1 class="main-title">교육 콘텐츠는 센터 회원 전용입니다</h1>
        <p class="sub-title">
            학원/학교 센터 코드로 가입하여<br>
            모든 학습 자료와 IDE 도구를 무제한으로 이용하세요
        </p>

        <div class="features-grid">
            <div class="feature-box locked">
                <div class="feature-title">
                    <i class="bi bi-book me-2"></i>Portal 학습자료
                </div>
                <div class="feature-desc">
                    Entry, Scratch, Python 등<br>
                    체계적인 교육 콘텐츠
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box locked">
                <div class="feature-title">
                    <i class="bi bi-play-circle me-2"></i>PongTube 강의
                </div>
                <div class="feature-desc">
                    전문 강사의 동영상 강의<br>
                    단계별 학습 가이드
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box locked">
                <div class="feature-title">
                    <i class="bi bi-code-square me-2"></i>IDE 도구
                </div>
                <div class="feature-desc">
                    Entry, Scratch, Python<br>
                    통합 개발 환경
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="feature-box locked">
                <div class="feature-title">
                    <i class="bi bi-check2-circle me-2"></i>문제 은행
                </div>
                <div class="feature-desc">
                    CT 문제, CosPro 모의고사<br>
                    자동 채점 시스템
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="cta-box">
            <div class="price-tag">월 110,000원 (학생 무제한)</div>
            <div class="cta-title">센터 회원으로 모든 기능 이용하기</div>
            <div class="cta-desc">
                ✓ 전체 교육 콘텐츠<br>
                ✓ Entry/Scratch/Python IDE<br>
                ✓ 2GB + 센터 공유 30GB 스토리지<br>
                ✓ 무제한 블로그 & 포트폴리오
            </div>
            <button class="btn btn-join" onclick="location.href='/center/join'">
                <i class="bi bi-key me-2"></i>센터 코드로 가입하기
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <button class="btn btn-back" onclick="history.back()">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-left me-2"></i>이전 페이지로
            </button>
        </div>

        <div class="mt-4">
            <small class="text-muted">
                센터 코드가 없으신가요? <a href="/center/inquiry" style="color: #667eea;">센터 문의하기</a>
            </small>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
